2. Metadata

The datasets contained in this repository consist of metadata extracted from publicly accessible cultural heritage platforms.

These metadata compilations are released as open data for research, educational, and digital humanities purposes.

3. Original Materials

All copyrights and intellectual property rights for the original materials, including but not limited to:

- books
- manuscripts
- images
- scans
- archival records
- institutional metadata

belong to their respective institutions, archives, libraries, museums, publishers, or other rights holders.

This repository does not claim ownership over the original materials.

4. Source Attribution

Users should always refer to the original source platforms and institutions when accessing or reusing original materials.

5. Project

This repository is part of the Open Data Armenia project, which aims to document Armenian cultural heritage collections preserved around the world.
